videos.headline: Freiermuth hauls in the Penn State TD
videos.description: Sean Clifford lobs it over the defense to Pat Freiermuth for the 16-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Freiermuth hauls in the Penn State TD) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Freiermuth muscles in for Penn State TD
videos.description: Penn State QB Sean Clifford tosses to TE Pat Freiermuth near the goal line and Freiermuth powers through multiple defenders for a TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Freiermuth muscles in for Penn State TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State's Toney blocks field goal
videos.description: Michigan State kicker Matt Coghlin attempts a 46-yard field goal, but Penn State DE Shaka Toney powers through the line to block it.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State's Toney blocks field goal) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clifford finds Hamler for wide-open Penn State TD
videos.description: Penn State QB Sean Clifford passes to a wide-open WR KJ Hamler, who then dives across the goal line for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford finds Hamler for wide-open Penn State TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State recovers muffed punt
videos.description: Michigan State WR Brandon Sowers muffs the punt and Penn State WR Dan Chisena recovers the ball inside the Spartans' 10-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State recovers muffed punt) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Freiermuth's TD widens Penn State's lead
videos.description: Sean Clifford quickly tosses to Pat Freiermuth, who gets into to the end zone for the touchdown to widen Penn State's lead over Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Freiermuth's TD widens Penn State's lead) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State's Brooks recovers fumble after ball richochet's off lineman
videos.description: Michigan State QB Brian Lewerke gets hit hard and loses the football. The ball stays in the air, bounces off OL Matt Allen and Penn State LB Ellis Brooks recovers it.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State's Brooks recovers fumble after ball richochet's off lineman) 2019/10/26 ESHEET
